Interface PaAttributeValueInstalledPackagesBuilder

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ImAttributeValueBuilder, TransmissionObjectBuilder<ImAttributeValue>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PaAttributeValueInstalledPackagesBuilderIetf

    public interface PaAttributeValueInstalledPackagesBuilder
extends ImAttributeValueBuilder
    Generic builder to build an integrity measurement installed packages attribute value compliant to RFC 5792. It can be used in a fluent way.
